  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <section data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n      <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"248\" data-backw=\"578\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"505086082\" data-ratio=\"0.4287037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bf14f6b3-78d3-4fd1-ed91-e83040cde500/public\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bf14f6b3-78d3-4fd1-ed91-e83040cde500/public\">\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </h3>\n  <h3 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <section data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n      <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: -1.2em 8px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\">\n         <br style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n        </p>\n        <p style=\"margin: -1.2em 8px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1em;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:inherit;\">新智元报道&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </h3>\n  <section style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\">编辑：peter东 乔杨</span>\n  </section>\n  <section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n     <h5 style=\"padding:10px;margin:10px 8px 0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;max-width:100%;word-break:break-all !important;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">【新智元导读】<span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Zep，一个为大模型智能体提供长期记忆的插件，能将智能体的记忆组织成情节，从这些情节中提取实体及其关系，并将它们存储在知识图谱中，从而让用户以低代码的方式为智能力构建长期记忆。</span></span></h5>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 24px;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">无论是ChatGPT还是Deepseek，随着大模型性能的提升，其能够处理的上下文也越来越长。但是，一旦超出上下文窗口的限制，大模型就需要重新开一个对话，如同「失忆」一般忘记之前交流的内容。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 24px;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然而，站在用户的角度，智能体应该能够记住之前的所有对话，因此如何有效地管理和利用对话历史，就成为了提升AI智能体用户体验的关键。拥有长期记忆后，智能体能够回忆过去的对话，减少幻觉、延迟和成本。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 24px;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">将聊天记录作为文本导入，然后使用RAG来「恢复记忆」，是一种让大模型具有长期记忆的常用方式，但这往往需要额外的工程，构建RAG也存在无法忽视的时间差。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 24px;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">最近，一家名为Zep AI的初创公司推出了为智能体打造的记忆层，通过回忆聊天历史，可以自动生成摘要和其他相关信息，使AI助手能够在不影响用户聊天体验的情况下，异步地从过去的对话中提取相关上下文。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin: 24px 8px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"141\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"452\" data-imgfileid=\"505084922\" data-ratio=\"0.25092592592592594\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9a1c7daa-f01f-43e6-4408-f60603d8fd00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1799\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9a1c7daa-f01f-43e6-4408-f60603d8fd00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 0px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">传送门：https://www.getzep.com/</span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 24px;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Zep AI成立于2023年，是一家位于湾区的YC系初创，主要愿景就是为AI构筑长期记忆。他们开发的核心插件已经在GitHub上开源，获得了3k+标星，同时也发表了详解技术原理的预印版论文。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin: 24px 8px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"296\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"1270\" data-imgfileid=\"505084921\" data-ratio=\"0.5277777777777778\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f6be65f7-7cfc-4bf4-6185-d9e4935ce700/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"2408\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f6be65f7-7cfc-4bf4-6185-d9e4935ce700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 0px;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">仓库地址：https://github.com/getzep/zep</span></p>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"></span>Zep：更适合工业界的MemGPT</p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <h2 style=\"margin: 24px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"></span></h2>\n  <section style=\"margin: 24px 8px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"233\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"558\" data-imgfileid=\"505084919\" data-ratio=\"0.41388888888888886\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/49105000-332d-4217-1fee-07c7180ca300/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1348\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/49105000-332d-4217-1fee-07c7180ca300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 0px;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">论文链接：https://arxiv.org/pdf/2501.13956</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 24px;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当前使用RAG的方法主要集中在领域知识和静态语料库上，即添加到语料库的文档很少发生变化。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 24px;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">要使智能体的落地场景更加普遍，解决各种各样琐碎或高度复杂的问题，就需要访问大量的动态数据，比如与用户的交互、相关的业务数据以及世界知识。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 24px;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Zep的开发者们认为，当前的RAG方法并不适合实现这一愿景；要想赋予智能体以动态、广泛的「记忆力」，需要让LLM驱动的智能体真正拥有存储部件。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 24px;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">事实上，这个想法并非Zep AI团队的原创。2023年，UC伯克利的研究者们发表的MemGPT就提出了这一点。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin: 24px 8px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"133\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"318\" data-imgfileid=\"505084920\" data-ratio=\"0.2361111111111111\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/02777a03-8041-40e0-f361-73f1c4cbb200/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1346\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/02777a03-8041-40e0-f361-73f1c4cbb200/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 0px;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">论文链接：https://arxiv.org/pdf/2310.08560</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 24px;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">具体来看，Zep可视为AI智能体的基本内存，由具有时间感知能力的知识图谱引擎Graphiti所驱动，可以摄入并综合结构化业务数据和非结构化的消息数据，并动态更新知识图，从而表征一个复杂、不断发展的世界。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 24px;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">与其他知识图引擎相比，Graphiti的一个关键不同是具有时间提取和边失效过程，从而具备了管理动态信息更新的能力。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 24px;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"316\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"505084923\" data-ratio=\"0.5625579240037072\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/62e0ae91-7397-4bc2-0f32-1f6904dbde00/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1079\" data-width=\"1920\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/62e0ae91-7397-4bc2-0f32-1f6904dbde00/public\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 24px;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">相比MemGPT，Zep更适用于工业界的生产场景，在内存检索机制的各方面性能上都有所提升，包括准确性、延迟和可扩展性。</span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"margin: 24px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">构建知识图谱</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 24px;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Zep的「记忆」由一个具有时间感知能力的动态知识图谱（temporally-aware dynamic knowledge graph）所驱动，可以表示为𝒢=(</span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Zep AI 推出创新型 AI 记忆插件，通过知识图谱技术，突破性地解决大模型长期记忆难题，显著提升 AI 智能体在工业场景中的记忆精度和响应速度。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Zep AI 推出创新型 AI 记忆插件，通过知识图谱技术，突破性地解决大模型长期记忆难题，显著提升 AI 智能体在工业场景中的记忆精度和响应速度。",
  "summary": "文章介绍了 AI 初创公司 Zep AI 推出的创新型 AI 记忆插件 Zep。该插件旨在解决大模型长期记忆受上下文窗口限制的问题，通过构建具有时间感知能力的动态知识图谱，将智能体的记忆组织成情节、提取实体关系，从而实现长期记忆。Zep 的知识图谱包含情节子图（保留原始输入数据）、语义子图（提取实体及其关系）和社区子图（表示具有较强关联的实体簇）三个层次，通过包含余弦相似度搜索、全文搜索和广度优先搜索的内存检索系统，能够高效地从图谱中挖掘最佳语境。实验结果表明，与传统方法相比，Zep 在精度和响应时间上均有显著提升，更适用于工业界的生产场景。",
